 class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1514em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">s</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord accent\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.9579em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span></span><span style=\"top:-3.2634em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"accent-body\" style=\"left:-0.1667em;\"><span class=\"mord\">^</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1514em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">o</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord accent\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.9579em;\"><span style=\"top:-3em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">θ</span></span><span style=\"top:-3.2634em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"accent-body\" style=\"left:-0.1667em;\"><span class=\"mord\">^</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1514em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">n</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n<h1>Experiments</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/096eabcd6d5de29ad93d01fd8256c67d/2ba58/lwf_table1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 19.270833333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/096eabcd6d5de29ad93d01fd8256c67d/a59e9/lwf_table1.webp 192w,\n/static/096eabcd6d5de29ad93d01fd8256c67d/0ca9f/lwf_table1.webp 384w,\n/static/096eabcd6d5de29ad93d01fd8256c67d/dc9b9/lwf_table1.webp 768w,\n/static/096eabcd6d5de29ad93d01fd8256c67d/e2c2f/lwf_table1.webp 1152w,\n/static/096eabcd6d5de29ad93d01fd8256c67d/0a2c0/lwf_table1.webp 1187w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/096eabcd6d5de29ad93d01fd8256c67d/3b721/lwf_table1.png 192w,\n/static/096eabcd6d5de29ad93d01fd8256c67d/66595/lwf_table1.png 384w,\n/static/096eabcd6d5de29ad93d01fd8256c67d/fe486/lwf_table1.png 768w,\n/static/096eabcd6d5de29ad93d01fd8256c67d/d2d74/lwf_table1.png 1152w,\n/static/096eabcd6d5de29ad93d01fd8256c67d/2ba58/lwf_table1.png 1187w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/096eabcd6d5de29ad93d01fd8256c67d/fe486/lwf_table1.png\"\n            alt=\"Table 1. AlexNet 기반 Single new task scenario\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>Table 1. AlexNet 기반 Single new task scenario</strong></p>\n<p>표1은 AlexNet을 기반으로 실험을 진행한 결과이다.</p>\n<p>Single new task scenario : ImageNet → VOC 는 ImageNet으로 학습된 모델을 VOC 모델로 학습시키는 것을 의미한다.</p>\n<p>Joint Training은 이전 task의 데이터를 사용하는 방식이기 때문에 이 실험의 upper bound로 설정되었다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>new task에 대해서 LwF가 대부분의 방식보다 좋은 성능을 보여준다.</p>\n<p>특히 Fine-tuning 방식 보다 더 좋은 성능을 보여주는 것은 regularization term이 이 후 task에 도움이 될 수 있음을 의미한다</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>old task에 대해서 fine-tuning이 가장 안 좋은 성능을 보이는 것을 알 수 있다. Fine-tuning은 shared parameter까지 학습하기 때문에 forgetting이 가장 많이 일어나기 때문이다.\r\n이전 task의 데이터를 사용하는 joint training의 경우 old task의 성능이 가장 잘 유지되는 것을 확인 할 수 있다.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8c5994e106662ead56edf86f8b0b477f/0ff2a/lwf_figure7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.020833333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/8c5994e106662ead56edf86f8b0b477f/a59e9/lwf_figure7.webp 192w,\n/static/8c5994e106662ead56edf86f8b0b477f/0ca9f/lwf_figure7.webp 384w,\n/static/8c5994e106662ead56edf86f8b0b477f/dc9b9/lwf_figure7.webp 768w,\n/static/8c5994e106662ead56edf86f8b0b477f/58ffc/lwf_figure7.webp 1138w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/8c5994e106662ead56edf86f8b0b477f/3b721/lwf_figure7.png 192w,\n/static/8c5994e106662ead56edf86f8b0b477f/66595/lwf_figure7.png 384w,\n/static/8c5994e106662ead56edf86f8b0b477f/fe486/lwf_figure7.png 768w,\n/static/8c5994e106662ead56edf86f8b0b477f/0ff2a/lwf_figure7.png 1138w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/8c5994e106662ead56edf86f8b0b477f/fe486/lwf_figure7.png\"\n            alt=\"Figure7. Visualization for both new and old task performance for compared methods, with different weight losses\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Figure7. Visualization for both new and old task performance for compared methods, with different weight losses</p>\n<p>위의 그림은 Loss에서 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\lambda_0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>값을 어떻게 설정 하느냐에 따른 성능을 보여주고 있다.</p>\n<p><span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>λ</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\lambda_0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">λ</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3011em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>얼마나 regularization을 많이 줄지를 설정해 줄 수 있다.</p>\n<p>이 값이 작을 수록 old task에 대한 performance가 떨어지고 newtask에 대한 performance가 증가한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 768px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1720f26d5b90d4617354a0aaa2631df9/0591a/lwf_myresult.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/1720f26d5b90d4617354a0aaa2631df9/a59e9/lwf_myresult.webp 192w,\n/static/1720f26d5b90d4617354a0aaa2631df9/0ca9f/lwf_myresult.webp 384w,\n/static/1720f26d5b90d4617354a0aaa2631df9/dc9b9/lwf_myresult.webp 768w,\n/static/1720f26d5b90d4617354a0aaa2631df9/25dae/lwf_myresult.webp 838w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/1720f26d5b90d4617354a0aaa2631df9/3b721/lwf_myresult.png 192w,\n/static/1720f26d5b90d4617354a0aaa2631df9/66595/lwf_myresult.png 384w,\n/static/1720f26d5b90d4617354a0aaa2631df9/fe486/lwf_myresult.png 768w,\n/static/1720f26d5b90d4617354a0aaa2631df9/0591a/lwf_myresult.png 838w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/1720f26d5b90d4617354a0aaa2631df9/fe486/lwf_myresult.png\"\n            alt=\"Untitled\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>내가 진행했던 프로젝트에서 LwF를 이용해 Forgetting을 줄여주었다. Generator 모델의 학습 자체가 최적화되지 않아 Accuracy가 잘 나오지는 않았지만 weight를 조절함에 따라 새로운 Task에 대한 성능과 Forgetting 정도를 조절 할 수 있음을 배웠다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Learning without Forgetting","summary":"Web Service for alumni of Chung-Ang University, Colleg of Software","date":"2023.12.25.","categories":null}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/Learning without Forgetting/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}